mistral.reason: High Life (2013) is not Hip hop music. High Life is a Ghanaian genre with West African and Afro-Diaspora roots that emerged in Ghana as part of the anti-colonial struggle, and it has spawned many varieties including Hip-Life, which is viewed as a direct musical descendant of both Hip-Hop and High-Life. However, Hip-Hop and High-Life are distinct genres with different origins, hence High Life (2013) cannot be Hip hop music.
